      "span_text": "We have generally low power to detect correlations between nuclear backgrounds and other phenotypes since we used 12 DGRP backgrounds. In spite of this, we were first able to verify that development time in our flies corresponded well to the only available development time data (female pupation time at 25°: r = 0.99, t = 19.52, P = 0.003; Figure S5A ) and female eclosion time (r = 0.99, t = 8.23, P = 0.014; Figure S5B ) [CITATION_1] ."
